questions.question:
What is the output of the following code?

for (int i = 0; i < 5; i++) {
    if (i == 2) {
        continue;
    }
    System.out.print(i + " ");
}

What is the output of the following code?

for (int i = 0; i < 5; i++) {
    if (i == 2) {
        break;
    }
    System.out.print(i + " ");
}

What is the output of the following code?

for (int i = 0; i < 10; i++) {
    if (i % 3 == 0) continue;
    if (i > 7) break;
    System.out.print(i + " ");
}

What is the output of the following code?

int x = 0;
while (x < 10) {
    x += 3;
    if (x > 7) break;
    System.out.print(x + " ");
}
System.out.println("x = " + x);

What is the output of the following code?

outer:
for (int i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
    for (int j = 0; j < 3; j++) {
        if (j == 1) {
            break outer;
        }
        System.out.print(i + "" + j + " ");
    }
}

What is the output of the following code?

outer:
for (int row = 0; row < 3; row++) {
    for (int col = 0; col < 3; col++) {
        if (col == 1) {
            continue outer;
        }
        System.out.print("(" + row + "," + col + ") ");
    }
}

What is the output of the following code?

int count = 0;
for (int i = 1; i <= 5; i++) {
    for (int j = 1; j <= 5; j++) {
        if (i == j) continue;
        count++;
    }
}
System.out.println("count = " + count);

What is the output of the following code?

int sum = 0;
do {
    sum += sum + 1;
} while (sum < 10);
System.out.println("sum = " + sum);

What is the output of the following code?

for (int i = 0; i < 3; i++) {
    for (int j = 0; j < 3; j++) {
        if (i == 1) break;
        System.out.print(i + "" + j + " ");
    }
}

What is the result of the following code?

int i = 10;
while (i > 0) {
    i -= 3;
    if (i == 4) continue;
    System.out.print(i + " ");
}

What is the output of the following code?

for (int i = 0; i < 5; i++) {
    if (i % 2 == 0) {
        continue;
    }
    System.out.print(i + " ");
    if (i == 3) {
        break;
    }
}

In the following code, how many times does the inner loop body execute in total?

outer:
for (int i = 0; i < 4; i++) {
    for (int j = 0; j < 4; j++) {
        if (j == 2) {
            continue outer;
        }
    }
}
